{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"b558d663b7","title":"对宣传第一批女飞行员问题的报告的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"323c273c06","index":0,"year":1952,"month":2,"day":27,"articleId":"b558d663b7"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji31","name":"毛泽东全集第31卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/31-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji31":{"comments":[{"id":"86a3f90271","publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"b558d663b7","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"毛泽东的这个批语写在人民革命军事委员会总政治部副主任肖华1952年2月27日给毛泽东的报告上：肖华在报告中说，据空军报称，航空学校最近毕业了一批女飞行员，她们已掌握驾驶运输机的技术。为在三八节配合宣传中国妇女积极参加国防建设，拟在3月8日以3至6架运输机在北京上空散发传单，派代表在北京市妇联召集的纪念会上讲话，并作适当的文字报道和拍摄新闻电影。3月8日，在首都某机场举行了庆祝第一批女飞行员“三八”起飞典礼，12时15分飞机从机场起飞，13时10分飞临天安门上空，与首都人民见面。"},{"id":"787d0f9173","publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"b558d663b7","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"周，指周思来。"}],"contents":[{"id":"2b686f14fb","type":"title","text":"对宣传第一批女飞行员问题的报告的批语则","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"b558d663b7"},{"id":"86a3f90271","type":"paragraph","text":"请周调查一下是否可行，如可，请告肖华办理。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"b558d663b7"},{"id":"787d0f9173","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"b558d663b7"},{"id":"ca61a6c538","type":"paragraph","text":"二月廿七日","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"b558d663b7"}],"page":{"id":"36a5b1b238","publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"b558d663b7","start":447,"end":447}}}},"__N_SSG":true}